Repository pages

Usage: gitfleet site [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  get     Get Pages site information for a repository.
  create  Enable Pages for a repository.
  delete  Disable Pages for a repository.
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --json           
      --debug          
      --theme <THEME>  [default: auto]
      --yes            
      --dry-run        
  -h, --help           Print help
